column5: Was wondering if anyone knew of any place still selling minnows in the Innisfil area? I need some for tomorrow, having minnows races at my jack and jill and the store in Lefroy I normally get them from no longer has them.
Rack and Reel?  The had em on Tuesday.
go to a pet shop and get a few feeder fish
Rack and Reel is a possibility didn't really want to have to go into Barrie

Innisfil Bait& Tackle  5460 yonge st. @ hwy 89 gilford, ont 705-790-7309 healthy scoop of minnows $5 leeches worms tackle rods& reels open 6 am/7 days a week  they have a great selection at great prices.
Thanks Skeeter, they still have them
No problem, just remember that the $5 a scoop is the winter price.
